data.description: Check out this 3/2/2 in the sought after community of The Verandahs. The Master bedroom has a nice walk in closet and large en suite master bathroom featuring double sink vanity, garden tub and separate shower stall. This home features sliding glass doors which will lead you out to the covered back patio and huge fully fenced back yard. This large lot backs up to a conservation and pond. The Verandahs is a gated community located less than 3 miles from the Suncoast Parkway making your commute super easy to most parts of Tampa! The community also has a wonderful community pool and playground. Close to shopping, dining, top rated schools and several golf courses and a short drive to the Gulf and the Hudson Beach area.
